# Ansible Deployment for RentEstate

This project contains Î‘nsible playbooks for installing and running  PostgreSQL and the Spring Boot application, as well as enabling Docker and updating the Kubernetes deployment.


## Start Database & Spring Boot
To start the Postgres database and the Spring Boot application, run:

ansible-playbook -i hosts.yaml playbooks/postgres.yaml
ansible-playbook -i hosts.yaml playbooks/spring.yaml

##Start with Docker
To run the application using Docker, execute:

ansible-playbook -i hosts.yaml playbooks/docker-spring.yaml

##Update on Kubernetes
To update the deployment on Kubernetes, run:

ansible-playbook -i hosts.yaml playbooks/k8s-update-spring-deployment.yaml